			.box.box-faq
				h3.box-title What is the deposit to reserve my date?
				.box-content
					p To secure your date, a $500 deposit is required. The deposit is applied to your total balance, which is due at your Final Meeting,(1-2 weeks before your event.

			.box.box-faq
				h3.box-title Can I move my date?
				.box-content
					p Yes! Just as long as your new date is available! If your new date is available you will be charted a $100 administrative fee to make the change. To change your event date:
					ol
						li Check your new date's availability on the event calendar on #[a(href="http://thelodgeattraverse.com") our website];
						li Request your new date #[em in writing];
						li and submit your payment of $100.

			.box.box-faq
				h3.box-title What is the cancellation policy?
				.box-content
					p The deposit is considered non-refundable. However, if we are able to rebook your date we will refund $400, which is your deposit minus a $100 administrative fee. #[em All cancellations must be made in writing.]

